<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV99">
<l>kāṭṭiṉāṉcey valviṉaippa yaṉṟaṉālma ṉantaṉai</l>
<l>nāṭṭivaittu nallavalla ceyyaveṇṇi ṉāreṉak</l>
<l>kēṭṭataṉṟi yeṉṉatāvi piṉṉaikēḷva niṉṉoṭum</l>
<l>pūṭṭivaitta veṉṉainiṉṉuḷ nīkkalpūvai vaṇṇaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[I] have heard that showing [me] the powerful sins I have committed,</l>
<l>Establishing [my] manas in the [inevitability of their] fruits, [Yama’s messengers]</l>
<l rend="indent">Are thinking of doing [to me] things that are not good.</l>
<l>O Piṉṉai’s Husband! [Do] not [do that], do not remove me—who had tied my life breath</l>
<l>to You—from You, o bilberry-hued [Lord]!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
